post_text:
Dear Parent/Guardian,
We are excited to announce that Achieve3000®—an innovative, proven-effective literacy program we are using in your child’s school—is available for your child to use over the holiday break. With your encouragement, your child
will be able to build critical literacy skills.
Achieve3000’s articles and activities are tailored to your child’s precise reading level. Using Achieve3000 is proven
to help your child make reading gains!
This holiday break, Achieve3000 has introduced a brand-new Holiday Boot Camp, a collection of articles on
especially interesting topics. The more lessons kids complete, the greater their reading gains! To motivate your child to keep reading, there’s an Achieve3000 contest called Make the Break, where students have a chance to win exciting prizes for completing lessons while school is out.
Students can use Achieve3000 on any device, anytime, anywhere. Your role in your child’s learning cannot be
underestimated. Please encourage your child to participate in the Holiday Boot Camp and Make the Break contest!
